text:
Milana Aleksandrovna Vayntrub (; Uzbek Cyrillic: Милана Александровна Вайнтруб; born March 8, 1987) is an Uzbekistan-born American actress and comedian. She plays the character Lily Adams in a series of AT&T television commercials.
Vayntrub is set to star as Squirrel Girl in the "New Warriors" television series set in the Marvel Cinematic Universe.
